default councils. That means putting people who use our services or live in our communities in control of the decisions that affect their lives. At its core it is about citizens, councillors and council staff working together to determine local outcomes and how best to deliver those. 
defaultLambeth
default has developed its own ambitious public service reform programme to become a cooperative council. 
